title: Profile Insignia wrong ranking
body: I'm Plat in Solo/Due queue and gold in flex queue, but i got a gold profile insignia? shouldn't it be a Plat Insignia on my profile? please fix thank you

replies.body: The season **just** ended, so it's going to take some time to get everyone's rewards out.  Nobody has received their season rewards yet, keep an eye on our [helpdesk thread ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk)for updates and hang tight!
